53
00:08:54,825 --> 00:08:57,702
- That my check?
- Mm-hmm.

54
00:08:59,496 --> 00:09:03,166
Now, if you do get
any free time to yourself,

55
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:06,127
that's my number there
down at the station.

56
