66
00:10:31,505 --> 00:10:33,381
You look like hell.

67
00:10:33,465 --> 00:10:36,217
Hey, it's
a fashion statement, man.

68
00:10:36,301 --> 00:10:40,221
Only statement
them clothes got to make is, "I look like hell."

69
00:10:40,305 --> 00:10:42,807
My bike's broken down
at Elkin's Grove.

70
00:10:42,891 --> 00:10:47,770
I was thinkin', uh,
maybe I could borrow your ratchet set?

71
00:10:47,855 --> 00:10:51,190
The Summit's got me
overhauling six damn Ski-Doos,

72
00:10:51,275 --> 00:10:56,320
three Cats, and two flatbed
snowmakers... by Monday.

73
00:10:56,405 --> 00:10:59,031
What's the hurry?
It must be 70 degrees out there.

74
00:10:59,116 --> 00:11:01,033
It's injun summer, boy.

75
00:11:03,912 --> 00:11:09,041
Before you know it, winter gonna be
tear-assin' through this town with no apologies.

76
00:11:09,126 --> 00:11:12,503
Aw, come on.
It barely pissed snow the last couple years. This whole town's ready to fold.

77
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:15,423
[Clears Throat]
Yeah, well, see, this year's gonna be different.

78
00:11:15,507 --> 00:11:18,509
Is that right?
Mm-hmm. Take my word.

79
00:11:18,594 --> 00:11:23,973
You're gonna wish your piece
of shit excuse for a motorcycle was one of these sweet rigs.

80
00:11:25,350 --> 00:11:29,020
So, uh, Moss, how 'bout the ratchet?

81
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:35,777
All right, maybe I'll put in
a couple hours over the weekend, lighten things up a bit.

82
00:11:35,861 --> 00:11:37,862
[Sighs]

83
00:11:40,157 --> 00:11:44,452
There's 12 sockets
in that set... 12‒

84
00:11:44,536 --> 00:11:46,746
